title: The kid died from Vex Phoebe poisoning?
subtitle: The Facebook bulletin claimed that a child died in his sleep after applying his mother-in-law, Vex Faborup, to calm his mother-in-law, but we found no evidence of the incident.

vclaim: A young Mexican mother's son was recently poisoned by the objective application of Vex Faboppro.
